  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability and PK/PD Study in Young Adult Patients With Childhood Onset Growth Hormone Deficiency (GHD).</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase IIb Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetic and Pharmacodynamic Profile of ARX201 Following Repeated Dosing to Young Adult Patients With Childhood Onset Growth Hormone Deficiency (GHD).</official_title>
