  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study to find the optimal dose of Growth Hormone Replacement in young adult patients
      suffering from childhood onset growth hormone deficiency (GHD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the safety, tolerability and
      pharmacodynamic response of three different ARX201 doses (PEG-ahGH) when administered
      repeatedly to young adult patients with childhood onset growth hormone deficiency (GHD).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
